1, Turn the tilt skilt on to 325F and let the skilt warm before use. In the mean time find all the spices and put them together in a mixing bowl. 2, Once the skilt is hot add the meat to the skilt and allow the meat to cook off until it's nice and brown (5-10). 3, add the spices to the meat. Taste and add more spices if desired. Remove from tilt skilt and put in a hotel pan to keep the meat warm until serving.
